enb_long_title: TWELFTH SESSION OF THE SUBSIDIARY BODIES OF THE UNFCCC
sentences: SBI Chair John Ashe (Antigua & Barbuda) opened SBI-12 on Monday, 12 June.
He noted important progress at the informal meetings the previous week.
Delegates adopted the agenda and the organization of work for the session (FCCC/SBI/2000/L.1).
